are the underlying pattern. An interaction making two sources of light from
a common tightly controlled source showed one viewed state to be correlated
with the other. While it has been said that the 'signal' between them
travels faster than light, it's not needed to say that. The light travels
at its own speed. The underlying pattern has no 'speed' at all, in any
traditional sense. My use of the term 'information' includes this
underlying pattern, as well as the manifest signal we get. I don't know
what else to call it, but I realise a better word would help.

